      <title>里约热内卢最臭名昭著的谋杀案六年后结案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/brazil-police-conclude-probe-on-councilwoman-marielle-franco-murdered-in-2018</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西警方逮捕了 2018 年刺杀里约热内卢女议员玛丽埃尔·佛朗哥 (Marielle Franco) 的主谋，她的暴力死亡震惊了巴西人，后来成为全国范围内打击有罪不罚现象的象征。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/brazil-police-conclude-probe-on-councilwoman-marielle-franco-murdered-in-2018</guid>
